entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="jpn" o="新しいインプラントをつけて以来、彼女の様子がおかしいのよ…" t="Ever since she chipped that new implant, she's been actin' crazy..." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="夜通しどすどす歩き回ったり、叫び声や笑い声をあげたりして…" t="Stomping around all night, screaming and laughing like a complete lunatic..." b="" a=""/>
Didn't you say that implant was just some BD scrolling tech?
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="そうよ。でもほら、彼女はいつも安物を選ぶでしょ…" t="Yeah, but, you know, she's always going for the discount option..." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="どこの誰が使ったかもわからない、中古のガラクタを買ったのかも。きっと変なのを掴まされたのよ…" t="She probably bought some second-hand scrap from who-knows-where and caught something nasty..." b="" a=""/>
So what? You gonna call the MaxTac on her now?
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="その時になったら、躊躇せずに呼ぶわよ" t="You better believe I'll call 'em if it comes to that." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="でもあの人、最初からおかしいと思ってたの…" t="Something wasn't right with her from the get-go..." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="あのアパートだって、わざわざギリギリまで待ってから、私たちに競り勝ったでしょ？" t="Remember when she outbid us on that apartment at the last second?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="これだからサイコ女は…" t="The sneaky psycho cunt..." b="" a=""/>
